  guid: e11dcad1-28b3-4a4a-a5cc-66f913b47bbe
  itemName: Note #3
  description: "Boss,\r\n\r\nThe eastern piece is secured. We hid it inside a recess
    in the wall-follow the east canal and climb up through it. You\u2019ll find the
    entrance there if you know where to look.\r\n\r\nRossi is holding this one alone.
    The others are posted at the far end, like you ordered.\r\n\r\nThe pieces remain
    separated. No chance of them being brought together.\r\n\r\nWe\u2019ll hold position
    until we hear from you.\r\n"
  icon: {fileID: 7509403117698529453, guid: 945f2a5ccec718842a0f13fe94a2b967, type: 3}
